00:15:49.000 --> 00:15:52.920
It makes no sense, and
it denigrates the medium

00:15:52.920 --> 00:15:54.170
to think of it in those terms.

00:15:54.170 --> 00:15:57.440
Now, this is one
of my favorite--

00:15:57.440 --> 00:15:57.940
- Yes!

00:15:57.940 --> 00:15:59.065
- --works of olfactory art.

00:15:59.065 --> 00:16:02.910
Isn't this freaking great?

00:16:02.910 --> 00:16:04.960
Becky told me I
